<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩١-<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> فَقَالَ عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ الْهَرَوِيُّ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">خمسٌ من كن فيه استوجبت خَمْسًا:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٦٨⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَوَّلُهُ:</span> إِذَا حَدَّثَ النَّاسَ لَمْ يَكْذِبْهُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِذَا وَعَدَهُمْ لَمْ يُخْلِفْهُمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِذَا ائْتَمَنُوهُ لَمْ يَخُنْهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَإِذَا خَالَطَهُمْ لَمْ يَظْلِمْهُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَإِذَا غَابَ عَنْهُمْ لَمْ يَغْتَبْهُمْ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ محمدٍ:</span> فَأَمَّا الَّذِي يَجِبُ لَهُ عَلَى النَّاسِ:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَنْ يُحِبُّوهُ بِقُلُوبِهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَأَنْ يَدْعُوا لَهُ بِأَلْسِنَتِهِمْ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والثالث:</span> أن يعينوه بأنفسهم.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">والرابع:</span> أن يواسوه بِأَمْوَالِهِمْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالْخَامِسُ:</span> أَنْ يُقِرُّونَ لَهُ بِالْفَضْلِ عَلَى أنفسهم.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>